OL,3,CGrand National horse Get On George
OL,4,Cdies on second race at Aintree
OL,6,FA second horse has died on the second
OL,7,Fday of the Grand National at Aintree.
OL,9,FGet On George was put down after it
OL,10,Fpulled up in the second race of the
OL,11,Ffinal day of the festival.
OL,13,FThe horse was quickly dismounted on
OL,14,Fcourse by jockey Jack Tudor and was
OL,15,Fassessed before the decision was made
OL,16,Fto put the six-year-old horse down.
OL,18,FIt is the second horse death at this
OL,19,Fmeeting with Gold Dancer put down
OL,20,Fafter winning the Mildmay Novices'
OL,21,FChase on Friday, 10 April.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
