OL,3,CGrand National horse Get On George
OL,4,Cdies on second race at Aintree
OL,6,FGet on George was contesting the
OL,7,FWilliam Hill Handicap Hurdle but
OL,8,Fpulled up after losing his action
OL,9,Faround the bend.
OL,11,FThe death toll at the Aintree Festival
OL,12,Fhas now risen to 69 horses since the
OL,13,Fyear 2000 according to Animal Aid
OL,14,Ffigures with 17 of these deaths
OL,15,Foccurring after racing in the Grand
OL,16,FNational.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
