FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1776010271
OL,3,CGrand National horse Get On George
OL,4,Cdies on second race at Aintree
OL,6,FEmma Slawinski, chief executive at the
OL,7,FLeague Against Cruel Sports, said:
OL,8,F"Year after year we see horses dying
OL,9,Fat Aintree for people's entertainment
OL,10,Fand a cheap bet. Sadly, Get On George
OL,11,Fis yet another victim of this
OL,12,Fheartless spectacle which flies in the
OL,13,Fface of animal welfare.
OL,15,F"The public and businesses should
OL,16,Fboycott the Aintree Festival, refuse
OL,17,Fto bet on the racing, and stop
OL,18,Fwatching the TV Coverage and
OL,19,Fadvertising which glosses over the
OL,20,Fanimal cruelty.
OL,26,@pD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1776010271
OL,3,CGrand National horse Get On George
OL,4,Cdies on second race at Aintree
OL,6,F"The government needs to act as the
OL,7,FBritish Horseracing Authority and
OL,8,FJockey Club is prioritising gambling
OL,9,Fprofits over the lives of the horses."
OL,11,FAn RSPCA spokesperson said: "It is
OL,12,Fincredibly sad to hear of the death of
OL,13,Fa second horse, six-year-old Get On
OL,14,FGeorge, at this year's Grand National
OL,15,FFestival at Aintree.
OL,17,F"His tragic death is the 43rd
OL,18,Fcompetitive horse-racing fatality in
OL,19,Fthe UK this year alone - and it is
OL,20,Fonly April - and the 26th at the Grand
OL,21,FNational Festival over the last decade.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@fO]sD@]OU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
