OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1776010271
OL,3,CGrand National horse Get On George
OL,4,Cdies on second race at Aintree
OL,6,F"The RSPCA continues to engage with
OL,7,Fthe horse-racing industry in the hope
OL,8,Fof seeing greater safety measures
OL,9,Fintroduced to the sport, and
OL,10,Fmeaningful improvements for equine
OL,11,Fwelfare both on and off the track.
OL,12,FWhilst we recognise - and welcome -
OL,13,Fthat efforts have been made to improve
OL,14,Fsafety at the Grand National in recent
OL,15,Fyears, sadly the fatalities on 10th
OL,16,Fand 11th April indicate these measures
OL,17,Fare not yet adequately protecting
OL,18,Fhorses from serious risk."
OL,26,@nD@AOU
